				<wikidot:authorName>Emojk</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>473432</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>So&#8230; how can we know what the content of the etching is, or for that matter what SCP-1674-3 looks like, if there is no exit once one has stepped through? Have subjects shouted what they saw to someone inside SCP-1674?<br /> I like this one, though, it has just the amount of detail needed to confound me.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
